{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回\"解脱\"讲述了丁鹏前往藏剑庐挑战谢晓峰的过程。在藏剑庐中，丁鹏与谢晓峰进行了一场关于武道境界的深刻对话。谢晓峰自困于藏剑庐十年，是为了摆脱燕十三第十五剑的桎梏，追求更高层次的剑道境界。丁鹏的出现，以兵不血刃的方式破了那一剑，使谢晓峰豁然贯通。谢晓峰告诉丁鹏，下次再来时，藏剑庐将不复存在，意味着他已经能够将那两座坟墓搬到心中，随处皆可修行。藏剑庐的四名剑奴在谢晓峰解脱后也获得了自由，他们决定放下剑，过平凡的生活。丁鹏对谢晓峰的境界充满敬意，同时也对四名剑奴淡泊名利的胸怀感到钦佩。章末，丁鹏离开藏剑庐，与阿古在神剑山庄中发现有人暗中窥视，为后续情节埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我这次是来找前辈挑战决斗的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我知道，已经很久没有人来找我决斗了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不是为了成名，是真正地想找前辈一决。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我知道，你最近已经是个大名人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "以我在刀上的造诣，我以为可以跟前辈的剑一较上下了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你太客气，你应该说可以击败我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是现在我却无法对前辈拔刀。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是为了我此刻手中无剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这倒不是，此刻任何人都可以杀死前辈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不错，我所以要在门口设置禁戒，不让人进来，因为在这里，我是个手无缚鸡之力的老人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "但是我知道，出了这个地方，我必然不是前辈的对手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "那也不一定，胜负是很难说的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我输了，打扰前辈，多谢前辈指点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你今年几岁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "二十八岁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你很年轻，我今年已经五十六了，可是我在四十岁那年，才建了这藏剑庐，你足足比我晚十八年。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是前辈在此已经十年了……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不！我在此地的时间并不多，经常还要出去走走，我这好动的习惯还是改不了，你比我幸运。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我比前辈幸运？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，我一直都在成功中，所以领受失败的教训太迟，你却一开始就遭受了挫折，因此以后的进境很难说了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "以后希望有机会再与前辈一战。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "欢迎，欢迎，但我们最好还是在此地相见。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你已进来过，藏剑庐就不能再算是个禁地了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我感到很抱歉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不必抱歉，你来的时候，此地还是藏剑庐，因为这个地方只有你和我知，你懂吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我懂，我一定记住这句话，不告诉任何人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "特别是我的女儿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她到底是不是前辈的女儿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "这门怎么开了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为丁公子已经由茅亭中见过主人又出来了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "你们已经知道了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "知道了，但还是要谢谢丁公子。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "谢谢我？这跟我有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是丁公子帮助主人走出藏剑庐的。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "我帮助你们主人，你没弄错吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不会错，多年来，主人一直困住一个问题，就是为了那一招剑式，那一招燕十三的第十五剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "我知道那一剑，但这一剑已经成为过去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，现在是已经过去了，在丁公子面前，它就不能算一回事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "我根本没有见过这一式剑法。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "丁公子见过了，我们四个人最后逼丁公子进来的就是那一招剑式。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "就是那一剑？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，就是那一剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "就是那一剑击败了天下第一剑客谢晓峰？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我们的造诣自然不能与当年燕十三大侠相提并论，但是我们施展的就是那一剑。",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "造诣不足，也能够施展那一剑吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "照理是不能的，但是我们十年来，就专攻那一式，没有其他的事务分心，因此也勉强能够施展了，而且那一式施展出来，本就是至杀无敌的，可是却挡不住丁公子神刀一击。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我毕竟还能够算是天下无敌的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "神剑山庄今后已经没有藏剑庐了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "没有了，也不必要了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "你们四个人以后也不必守在这儿了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，丁公子不但帮助了主人，而且也使我们得到了解脱。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "今后四位是否还留在这儿呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "刚才谢小姐也希望我们留下，可是我们拒绝了，神剑山庄并不适合我们。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "什么地方才适合你们呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "有很多的地方，我们原先是为剑而生，以剑为生，因剑而生的，现在我们可以摆下剑，有很多的事都可以做，比如说，我最喜欢花，可以去做个花匠，乙丑喜欢养鱼，他可以去开个渔场，专心一意养他的鱼……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "你们要放下剑来？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，我们要放下剑来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "你们可知道，如果你们不放下剑，在江湖上，立刻可以享受无限的尊荣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我们知道，主人说过，我们若是出去了，当世很少有敌手，我们立可成为一流的高手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "难道你们不想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我们虽然很想，可是有一个难题，成为江湖一流高手后，就没有时间做我们喜欢的事了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "丁公子可以看得出，我们的年纪不小了，也可以说是过去了半辈子，上半辈子是为剑而活了，下半辈子可不能再为剑了，我们要为自己而活。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "你们的生活都有了安排吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "有的，主人在建立这藏剑庐时，就给了我们每人五万一千二百两银子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "这是一笔很不小的财产了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这只是第一年的费用。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "这还是第一年的，那十年下来，你们每个人所得，岂非已经是数都数不清了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不，数得清，而且很快就可以数清了，因为就只有一块，一百两重的一块。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "就只有一块，一百两？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，主人实在很慷慨大方。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "你们几个人头脑是否有问题？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "没有，我们很正常，头脑也很清楚。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "那就是我的头脑有问题了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "丁公子的头脑也没问题，只是不知道主人跟我们的约定而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "哦！你们的主人是如何跟你们约定的。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "主人跟我们的约定是我们留此一年就想离开，就可以带走五万一千二百两，留到第二年，就只有两万五千六百两，如此，每年减一半，到现在是十年，因此刚好是一百两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "这是哪一门子的算法？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这是主人给我们的算法，如果我们在此只留一年，剑术未精，心气又浮，必须要那么多的银子，才能够安安稳稳地过日子，否则不是沦为盗贼，就是走人歧途，才能满足自己的欲望。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "这倒好像有点道理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "主人一向是有道理的。",
      "tone": "尊敬",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "只不过我若再晚几年来，你们岂非只有一两银子了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，我们若能再追随主人几年，就是一两银子没有，我们也能安之若素，生活得很愉快了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "这么说我倒是来得太早了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "在我们而言，虽然希望多追随主人几年，但是再想到能够让主人早早走出这一层屏障，更上层楼，这点牺牲倒也值得。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "不错，的确值得，的确值得。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "你们如若感到银子不够……",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不！不！我们觉得很够了，因为我们的愿望都很简单，很容易满足，而且在这十年中，我们也都养成了劳动的习惯，所以出去后，我们不但用不了这一百两银子，或许过个三五年，还能再赚下一百两银子呢。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "甲子，你们跟我没关系，本来用不着我来替你们操心，只不过我想谢晓峰今后可能没多少精神来照顾你们了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，主人说过，他要远离个一两年，去访问几个老朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "哦？去得很远吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "很远，很远，据说是要深人大漠，穷尽荒边。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "甲子，外面的世界，并不像你们所想像的那么单纯，除非你们是真正的平凡的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "甲子",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我们懂，我们如果有不可开交的问题时，一定会来请求丁公子帮忙的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_jia_zi",
      "text": "再见。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_a_gu",
      "text": "阿古，这些人跟着我们已经很久了，我很不喜欢。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    }
  ],
